main event: An unidentified flying object was observed in Cincinnati, Ohio, for approximately 5 minutes on November 11, 1966.
interesting points: The object appeared solid and blue-white in color., The sighting was made during clear night conditions., The object moved behind a cloud at one point during the observation., The witness reported that the object did not make any sound., A hand-drawn sketch showing the object's shape and movement was included in the report.
